Can I interact to PX4 and Gazebo with standard C++ no gui?

Yes. In fact, **this is one of the most common ways** to develop robotics applications. You can control both **PX4** and **Gazebo** using **standard C++** without creating any GUI.

## Architecture

```text
             +-----------------------+
             |   Your C++ Program    |
             | (Standard C++17/20)   |
             +-----------+-----------+
                         |
               MAVLink / MAVSDK
                         |
                 UDP/TCP Connection
                         |
                     PX4 SITL
                         |
                  Gazebo Simulation
                         |
                    Simulated Drone
```

Your C++ application is just a console application.

---

## What you can do

### Connect to PX4

```cpp
int main()
{
    // connect
    // arm
    // takeoff
    // land
}
```

No GUI needed.

