## Gazebo interaction

Besides talking to PX4 through MAVLink/MAVSDK, Gazebo itself exposes APIs and transport messages that C++ programs can use.

You can:

* Spawn models
* Delete models
* Move objects
* Read world state
* Pause simulation
* Resume simulation
* Reset world
* Change simulation speed

